  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 46e03a19f8e5e124dad137a0f14696cc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dialogue Day 1 Faction Member
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - "Hey\u2026 You"
  - "You\u2019re the father of that town favourite \u201Coh so beloved\u201D daughter,
    aren\u2019t you?"
  - "You\u2019re the same as me, yet you\u2019re sit here diligently carrying out
    every last bidding of those government fucks like some pathetic, clueless pawn."
  - "You: I-I\u2019m sorry I don\u2019t quite understand what you\u2019re say-"
  - "Yeah, fancy that isn\u2019t it? You would never say shit about them, would you? 
    After all, what have they ever done to you?"
  - "We\u2019re the same age\u2026 you remember that day\u2026. maybe not fully,
    but well enough. "
  - "That day where they \u201Csaved us from the other government who kidnapped our
    parents\u201D, you remember life before it, don\u2019t you? YOU KNOW THAT ISN\u2019T
    THE FULL TRUTH, DON\u2019T YOU? SOMETHING ELSE HAPPENED, DIDN\u2019T IT?"
  - "DEEP DOWN, YOU DON\u2019T TRUST THEM EITHER, DO YOU!?!?"
  - 'You: ...'
  - "\u2026. Fuck it, pointless trying to get through to one of you brainwashed slaves."
